Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, it's time to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.47,0:00:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.44,0:00:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ngaah~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.24,0:00:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and start already!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.86,0:01:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while since I last wore my uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.50,0:01:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's Kona-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.59,0:01:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Kona-chan, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.29,0:01:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Kagami-san, Tsukasa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.85,0:01:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A very good morning to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.50,0:01:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, Tsukasa-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.68,0:01:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Your ribbon is not quite straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.83,0:01:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.01,0:01:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ew.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.98,0:01:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Kona-chan, what happened to you all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.33,0:01:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.93,0:02:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been addicted to Marimite lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.82,0:02:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Marimite?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.90,0:02:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.43,0:02:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,don't go around dressing like them, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.37,0:02:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, is that cosplay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.52,0:02:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I wouldn't go that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.78,0:02:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.65,0:02:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I do enough of that at my part-time job.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.83,0:02:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, you work at a place that does that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.42,0:02:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But if Kona-chan dressed up like a proper lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.25,0:02:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so weird that I can't even imagine it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.09,0:02:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Lately, baseball games going to extra innings have really gotten out of hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.40,0:02:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do the late-night anime viewers have to be the ones that get shafted?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.80,0:02:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to watch anime that much,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.84,0:02:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,why don't you just get cable?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't they have dedicated channels for that stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.39,0:02:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe me, if I could have,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.96,0:02:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I already would have...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.52,0:02:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But the cable TV guy said that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.86,0:02:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...he couldn't run a cable to my house...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.15,0:03:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki-chan, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.38,0:03:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Tsukasa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.73,0:03:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You look bummed-out... Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.99,0:03:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I went to get my tooth looked at, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.38,0:03:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you went to the dentist?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.95,0:03:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Good for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.01,0:03:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it that when you go to the dentist once, you have to keep coming back for so many follow-ups?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.57,0:03:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I totally understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.74,0:03:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never gone to a dentist fewer than two times per occasion!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.61,0:03:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki-san, how do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.34,0:03:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Konata-san, how are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.02,0:03:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you been doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.75,0:03:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Splendid, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.60,0:03:38.86,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to see you are doing well yourself, Konata-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.51,0:03:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, that's Yuki-chan for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.12,0:03:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Honorific dialogue doesn't seem to perturb Miyuki-chan at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.56,0:03:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Or rather, she doesn't find Kona-chan's words odd at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.30,0:03:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen anyone greet people with "how do you do".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? {"Really?", "Huh?"}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.31,0:03:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.48,0:03:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,At the all-girls high school to which my friend goes,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.02,0:03:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,they greet each other like this on a regular basis.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.51,0:04:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A high school for true upper-class ladies is quite different, wouldn't you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How genteel of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuroi told me to collect all the summer vacation homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.64,0:04:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How genteel of you, Sebastian.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.50,0:04:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sebastian?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A butler just has to be called "Sebastian".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.68,0:04:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I have that image, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Say something funny, Sebastian.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.88,0:04:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I know summer vacation has just ended, but you don't have time to space out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.32,0:04:25.86,Signs,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.32,0:04:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You should think about your future and focus on your studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.86,0:04:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Our future... Like what we'll be doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.01,0:04:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess high school is just one stop along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't really thought about the future, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.49,0:04:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.15,0:04:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.45,0:04:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you even chose humanities just so you could be in the same class as us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.21,0:04:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsu-Tsukasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You told them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.20,0:04:45.52,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Ah, sowwy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.39,0:04:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And to her, of all the people!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, just be honest with yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.86,0:04:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You just don't want to be alone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.11,0:04:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.61,0:04:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.79,0:05:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.89,0:05:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I came over again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.45,0:05:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Nee-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.32,0:05:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I did my summer homework like you told me to...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.40,0:05:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And filled in all the blanks with what looked like the answers...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.19,0:05:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, she's making me redo it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.14,0:05:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Uh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.82,0:05:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.10,0:05:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If you ask me, you might have to turn it in again...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.91,0:05:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You weaseled out of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.22,0:05:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,My summer vacation doesn't get extended, but my homework does...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.38,0:05:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should ask Kagami for her notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.36,0:05:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The cicadas sound soothing, just like a lullaby.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.77,0:06:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... Extra innings pushed it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.19,0:06:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess that's helpful sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.75,0:06:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The recording times are off, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.87,0:06:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.70,0:06:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki-chan, where are your glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.42,0:06:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I accidentally broke them this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.59,0:06:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot I put them on my chair...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.60,0:06:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I accidentally...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.65,0:06:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize but, do you think I can copy your notes for today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.09,0:06:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.94,0:06:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You have that "klutzy" look down pat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Konata-san, your writing is interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.86,0:06:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa-san, fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Those guys really are useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.79,0:06:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.56,0:06:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.20,0:06:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a good thing we had the same teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.32,0:06:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.15,0:07:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you keep this a secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.18,0:07:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't want to hurt their feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.84,0:07:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.56,0:07:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki-chan, let's have lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.04,0:07:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Tsukasa-san, Konata-san, thank you for your notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.08,0:07:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to thank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.27,0:07:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought I would ever loan Yuki-chan my notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.22,0:07:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I doubt you ever will again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.59,0:07:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um, is there something on my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,In games, when the "glasses" character comes to school without them... {...When the character with glasses...}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.48,0:07:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They suddenly become popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.44,0:07:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that doesn't actually happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.62,0:07:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't think it does, unfortunately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.76,0:07:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Choco cornets look kind of like drills.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.34,0:07:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Drills?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Speaking of which,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.91,0:07:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't we have a discussion about which side of a choco cornet is the head?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.97,0:07:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The skinny side kind of looked like the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.89,0:07:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.86,0:07:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I look at it, the fat side looks like the butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.43,0:07:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Butt?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.89,0:08:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.86,0:08:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's some junk in the trunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.15,0:08:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention the layered fat rolls on the stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.41,0:08:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,When you gain weight on the lower half,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.65,0:08:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't it troubling when you try to buy skirts and stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.56,0:08:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.73,0:08:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If you try to get one that fits your waist, then your hips don't fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.34,0:08:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you get one that fits your hips, it fits loosely around your waist.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.94,0:08:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Having no other choice, you buy the one with the loose-fitting waist.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.17,0:08:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you're walking around, it spins around and around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.82,0:08:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.72,0:08:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A body with a layered stomach, cornet-type.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.14,0:08:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If you turn it on this side,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.44,0:08:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,it becomes a lazily sleeping body, gorone-type.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.70,0:08:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,When you turn it back up, cornet-type.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.09,0:08:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even know where I'm supposed to laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.07,0:08:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, didn't you go on a diet to lose the weight you gained during summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.95,0:08:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I lost weight but my waist and hips are still the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.87,0:08:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But Kagami, I can clearly see the progress of your diet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.37,0:08:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.51,0:08:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, so clearly that I could grab it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.94,0:08:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,When you go on a diet, you tend to first lose weight in the areas you really don't want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.57,0:08:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.75,0:08:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Say no more!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,When you read a sentence, always keep in mind what the overall message is,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.79,0:09:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and what the author is trying to convey to his audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.33,0:09:09.73,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,I see how it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.76,0:09:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I heard that people with poor vision tend to glare a lot and scare other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.31,0:09:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I think that depends on the person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.12,0:09:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,When you said "depends on the person",
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.12,0:09:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,you looked my way, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.53,0:09:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I've also heard that you look prettier when you make your eyes thinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.64,0:09:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes your eyes look more luscious...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.03,0:09:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, we don't have to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.52,0:09:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Late!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.28,0:09:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck is Konata doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.75,0:09:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, she's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.31,0:09:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.48,0:09:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Way late!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.51,0:09:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always complaining about how extra innings are too long, and now you're late?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.09,0:09:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know, there have been so many games going to extra innings that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.40,0:09:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...I think I caught it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.26,0:09:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not contagious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So why are you late?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.98,0:09:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Overslept?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.77,0:10:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, I'm not a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.25,0:10:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, give me an adult reason why you're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.82,0:10:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,After I readied-up, I had quite a bit of spare time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.58,0:10:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So to kill time, I played some games,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.72,0:10:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but then I couldn't find a good saving point...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.34,0:10:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the worst...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.33,0:10:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Worse than a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.84,0:10:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,there are a lot of festivals like the culture and sports festivals in the second semester.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.44,0:10:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention that we have tests as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.84,0:10:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Kona-chan, you're so athletic that you can do well in the sports festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.86,0:10:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like sports festivals because they tire me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.97,0:10:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen someone athletic who hates manual labor this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.02,0:10:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what our class is doing for the culture festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.37,0:10:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not like there is really anything to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.08,0:10:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty hard to decide these things unless someone is really motivated to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.72,0:10:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And the one that comes up with suggestions is responsible for most of the work, so no one steps up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.36,0:10:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to stay after class and prepare.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.44,0:10:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't make it home in time to watch evening anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.87,0:10:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you were going to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.97,0:11:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in charge of dinner tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.88,0:11:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,so I have to go shopping on the way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.84,0:11:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to make?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.14,0:11:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's favorite chicken curry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,My family loves chicken.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.83,0:11:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Curry, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.18,0:11:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.02,0:11:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, they say curry tastes better when you let it sit overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.13,0:11:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.75,0:11:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll make a little extra and bring some to class for lunch tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.99,0:11:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I'll have leftovers, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.75,0:11:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, this is the Hiiragi residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.91,0:11:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Tsukasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.01,0:11:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Kona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.43,0:11:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it this early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.81,0:11:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that curry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.18,0:11:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.23,0:11:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The curry I made yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I let it sit overnight and now it's spoiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.33,0:11:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.10,0:11:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.98,0:11:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.87,0:11:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.98,0:11:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Curry shouldn't go bad overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.40,0:11:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.45,0:11:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you put something weird in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.17,0:11:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There was mold all over it this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.44,0:11:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A cornet again today?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.33,0:12:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They taste good so I don't really mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.18,0:12:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's okay with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.51,0:12:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I just realized this,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.86,0:12:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,but there are times when Tsukasa and Kagami's lunches are really elaborate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.64,0:12:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{made properly... (as per a.f.k. script)} {might need a doki TL to be safe}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.99,0:12:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And other times, they can be rather simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a clear distinction.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.19,0:12:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, Tsukasa and I take turns in making lunch,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.11,0:12:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm not that good with household chores,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.13,0:12:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,so my lunch ends up being simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.79,0:12:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, sorry for that being the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.56,0:12:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami, are you the type that blows pots up when you try to cook?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.20,0:12:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think people like that exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.84,0:12:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki-chan, like always, your lunches look really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.70,0:12:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I just stuffed in yesterday's leftovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.52,0:12:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki-san's dinner is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.50,0:12:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This extravagant?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.22,0:12:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,These are "leftovers"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.36,0:12:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, what's inside these eggs?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.76,0:12:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I had some leftover eel last night, so I tried putting it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.40,0:12:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you ever have leftover eel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.62,0:13:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The only leftovers ever in our house are moldy curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.70,0:13:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I never considered your house to be "normal".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.03,0:13:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.13,0:13:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.01,0:13:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.03,0:13:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.55,0:13:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,My parents got me a cell phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.95,0:13:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.36,0:13:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I happened to score highly on the standardized tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me your number and I'll give you mine in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.06,0:13:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What was my number again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.27,0:13:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a second, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.05,0:13:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Konata, you had a cell phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.64,0:14:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, but I usually forget it at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.18,0:14:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because the only person who calls me is my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.85,0:14:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what's the point of you having a cell phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.61,0:14:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.27,0:14:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Keroro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.56,0:14:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.86,0:14:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.98,0:14:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They bought it along with my cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, there's a girl in our class who has a bunch of straps.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.66,0:14:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,When she weighed them, the straps alone came to a total of 800 grams.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.01,0:14:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That much?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.77,0:14:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.02,0:14:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,When she took her straps off, her pain in the shoulder went away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.03,0:14:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds like too much of a workout just to talk to someone on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.95,0:14:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cell phones excite you because you never know when someone will call you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.45,0:14:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.29,0:14:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope someone calls me soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.87,0:14:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you get so excited over a cell phone, nowadays?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.64,0:14:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, did you figure out your number?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.39,0:14:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um, not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.83,0:14:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,In England, there was a great civil war between the Lancastrians and Yorkists.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.90,0:14:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The two houses wore red and white roses, respectively, when they fought.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.53,0:15:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus, people refer to this war as the "War of Roses".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.05,0:15:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It lasted from 1455 to 1485.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.44,0:15:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.43,0:15:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.19,0:15:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.32,0:15:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my cell phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.35,0:15:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally got a call!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.07,0:15:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.97,0:15:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm taking this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.46,0:15:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Come get it in my office after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.85,0:15:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad that she gave it back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.90,0:15:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would've thought you'd get spam this early?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.22,0:15:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.14,0:15:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm still at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.36,0:15:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm late because I was talking to Miyuki and Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.68,0:15:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.20,0:15:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be going home soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.82,0:15:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.73,0:15:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what happens when I'm a little late.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.84,0:15:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.84,0:15:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.61,0:15:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.17,0:15:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, still at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.95,0:16:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm with Kona-chan and everyone right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.28,0:16:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.79,0:16:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you only have to call one daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.65,0:16:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's natural for dads to be worried about their daughters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you get a lot of spam mail lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.16,0:16:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If you make your address something unusual, you can avoid that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.79,0:16:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.45,0:16:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Something unusual?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.85,0:16:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Like how?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.19,0:16:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My address is in romaji...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.37,0:16:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's superglassesgurlzlove@~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.07,0:16:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,At first I wanted to pick maids or shrine maidens, but those are too popular so{\fscx300}- {Em-dash added due to interruption in the next line. This line needs to be re-checked. The timing should be longer.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.12,0:16:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.59,0:16:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it, so please don't say stuff like that out in public.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.43,0:16:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This conversation is even more disturbing than all the spam mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.22,0:16:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.67,0:16:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.05,0:16:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Tsukasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.11,0:16:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,My cell phone... My cell phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,She left it in her pocket and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.19,0:17:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone to a better place, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.42,0:17:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if they'll buy me another one?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.41,0:17:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So this guy was okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.06,0:17:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What a tough little dude...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So that text message last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.71,0:17:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The one that said, "Kagami said you didn't give her notebook back yet."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.56,0:17:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that the last one you sent?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.30,0:17:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you happen to respond?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.76,0:17:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.18,0:17:29.56,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,You probably don't respond to mails you get right away, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.56,0:17:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I usually don't reply to people I see everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.18,0:17:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You should return text messages with text messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.68,0:17:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you guys everyday so I thought it was unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.96,0:17:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to lose your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.64,0:17:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.73,0:17:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that big of a deal...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.23,0:17:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't decide that on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.71,0:17:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, she never returned my notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.46,0:17:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa, I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.17,0:18:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.26,0:18:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.62,0:18:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so moved by the manga I borrowed from Kona-chan that I started crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.22,0:18:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.44,0:18:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Kona-chan, thanks for the manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.13,0:18:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It was really interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It was so ridiculous that it made you want to laugh, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.53,0:18:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.47,0:18:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I cried because I was so touched.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe they're talking about the same manga with such wildly different response.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.32,0:18:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If you cry you're, like, Tsukasa and if you laugh you're, like, me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.35,0:18:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.62,0:18:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be categorized like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.86,0:18:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see your reaction, Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.76,0:18:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it such a crime to want to know more about your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.36,0:18:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, did you cry or laugh during Attack No.1?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.10,0:18:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HD13D7D&\2c&HEBA3C3&\c&HFFFFFF&}Cried.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.10,0:18:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\2c&HAC6F4A&\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HCA5F27&}Laughed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, what's your favorite manga?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.13,0:18:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Keroro Gunso!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.96,0:18:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,These two...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.59,0:18:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure if they're similar or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.09,0:18:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Kona-chan, aren't you going to join the manga research club?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You like manga and the ilk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.42,0:18:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I wouldn't mind joining...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.34,0:18:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And I hear the meeting times are flexible as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.72,0:19:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,*draw draw* *draw draw*
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.39,0:19:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you even trying when you drew this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.58,0:19:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.62,0:19:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly did you try to draw, Konata-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.49,0:19:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.27,0:19:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This is me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.53,0:19:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Miyuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.02,0:19:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, giving you a huge margin of error, I guess I can see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.59,0:19:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.86,0:19:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... So I breathe fire now, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.33,0:19:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.79,0:19:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami-san, you're just the person I imagined you to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.18,0:19:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.14,0:19:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I said stop that already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.19,0:19:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, there's a new volume of Full Metal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.00,0:19:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, it's coming out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.29,0:19:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm stopping by Gamers, do you want to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.86,0:19:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I'm gonna go to the local bookstore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.20,0:19:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And there are some things of which I have to take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.13,0:19:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the part where you and I are supposed to go together and deepen our friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.82,0:19:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with you today?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.82,0:19:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.41,0:19:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, the word "friendship" doesn't fit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.44,0:19:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,As a symbol of our friendship, I wanted your purchase points.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.66,0:19:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is your "friendship", huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.32,0:19:58.95,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,{\fs45}Wait for me just a little more...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.90,0:20:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.16,0:20:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so quiet...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.87,0:20:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she mad at me for mixing up my twintail ribbons with sunflowers?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.34,0:20:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.31,0:20:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What, me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.67,0:20:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,To Akira-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.60,0:20:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.48,0:20:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.19,0:20:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, it's already started...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.86,0:20:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap, I have to do something before the channel changes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.81,0:20:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oha-lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.36,0:20:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Or, I tried saying that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.08,0:20:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky Channel has started once again this week!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.99,0:20:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiraishi Minoru here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.83,0:20:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Since Akira-sama is in a foul mood...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.45,0:20:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Saying your name before that of Kogami Akira...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.57,0:20:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't understand anything about the hierarchy, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.35,0:20:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,T-That's not what I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.09,0:21:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been using those twintails quite a bit lately, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.61,0:21:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Using them?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.44,0:21:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get too full of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.40,0:21:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.99,0:21:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, in the "Let's make Akira look prettier" plan, everyone was hoping to see my twintails, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.16,0:21:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.24,0:21:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.91,0:21:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going with twin drills now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.95,0:21:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Twin drills?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.97,0:21:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate the Getter's speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.66,0:21:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Number two. The age of twintails is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.04,0:21:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The next fad is: twin drills!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.08,0:21:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Konata said so in episode 2,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.94,0:21:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,"Drills are every man's ultimate fantasy."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.08,0:21:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Fantasy, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.17,0:21:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then everyone, we'll continue on with the radio and homepage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.88,0:21:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Look forward to next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.29,0:21:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bii.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.43,0:21:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.17,0:21:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.64,0:21:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Those twintails.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.07,0:21:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the ones I have?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.26,0:21:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.88,0:21:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The ones you did in real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.02,0:21:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.45,0:21:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They had sunflowers on them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.53,0:21:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, they did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.58,0:21:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I've seen that somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.31,0:21:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.28,0:21:58.22,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,How many years back was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.16,0:21:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It was one of my...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.55,0:21:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ew! Disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.81,0:22:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, I was so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.02,0:22:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It was really cute, I enjoyed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.19,0:22:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you get nervous singing your first song of the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.02,0:22:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know if you can sing it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.80,0:22:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Next is Miyuki's turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.35,0:22:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I want her to sing something sentimental.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.20,0:22:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.28,0:22:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, may I have the mic?
